{"type": "article", "id": 33901, "title": "往里看，这信封里藏着一个“小宇宙”｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-30T23:24:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 34438, "name": "Stone Designs"}, {"id": 34439, "name": "The House of Marley"}, {"id": 4549, "name": "Steelcase"}, {"id": 34440, "name": "Makeblock"}, {"id": 34441, "name": "B.Lux"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 199, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161030232709tuHBzhFPvJUeT2so.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p>          </p><h3>Starry Sky Envelope by Moe Tsukada</h3><p>你还记得因为收到纸质信件而获得的喜悦吗？你还记得上一次看到星空是什么时候吗？日本设计师 Moe Tsukada 带来的 Starry Sky 信封想让你感受到两倍的惊喜。从外表看，它和常规的信封没什么太大的区别，只是多了厚厚的黑色内衬。不过，当你对着灯往里面瞄的时候，信封内部就变成了一个散发着点点星光的小宇宙，相当浪漫。这是它的<a href=\"http://shop.spoon-tamago.com/collections/stationery/products/starry-sky-envelope\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 12 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030232624pGqMY7DvVfx5SHOB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610302326226BWIl4JYPVX97MuK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030232622Fsktzxm36Vf8SvgK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030232622YHWe5M9i1LC4sl8G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030232624agPlc8qCLZAniyfT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030232624rPug8K4ZY3WHlBDa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.791841\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Airblock by Makeblock</h3><p>无人机对我们来说已经不是什么遥不可及的产品了，来自深圳的科技公司 <a href=\"http://www.makeblock.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Makeblock</a> 打算让它变得更酷一点。这台叫 Airblock 的模块化无人机不仅允许你自己动手拼出自己想要的形态，还能通过可视化编程的方式自定义飞行特技。Airblock 由借助磁性相连的零件构成，主要采用轻量且抗震的 EPP/PP 环保材料制作，会最大程度减缓撞击。更让人惊喜的是它的操作方式：通过蓝牙配对之后，你可以在专属的应用上进行可视化编程，让它做出各种神奇的动作。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1818505613/airblock-the-modular-and-programmable-starter-dron\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 99 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610302048394wNRcQkOCYX5IePu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.486765\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030204845xuSbgnTNamydlX3e.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564286\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030204843MeDUHQrFS24lZbNE.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.803571\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030204843NWkFvTcDe2xVdEAo.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560714\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Navi TeamIsland by Steelcase</h3><p>不蹲格子间的开放式办公环境，普通的办公桌很难同时满足私密性和必要时的团队协作，为此家具公司 <a href=\"https://www.steelcase.com/asia-zh\" rel=\"nofollow\">Steelcase</a> 带来了这款名为 <a href=\"https://www.steelcase.com/asia-zh/products/meeting-tables/navi-teamisland/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Navi TeamIsland</a> 的办公桌生态系统。办公桌通过轻量化的可调节屏风划分个人空间；除了私人抽屉之外，位置下方的桌脚和桌角上方的空间都可以用来存放个人物品；在需要视频通话的场合，翻盖板和桌子的衔接边缘还可以用作设备底座。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610302117110PLcaxpSQyRtBfHD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654426\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030211709fKXOiWcFn0lrsUpH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.766031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030211710sZvCI1fgtXP5LQro.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664537\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030211711qCLmy4aJek7dXr0I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666029\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610302117103w8TH2bc5fndFNCJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563745\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Talon by Chijoff+Co</h3><p>一些生活中的小麻烦有时会让你手忙脚乱：比如本来只是要把螺丝拧回去，却在不知不觉间浪费了好多时间在找工具，最后还得把它放回本来的地方。来自澳大利亚设计团队 Chijoff+Co 为此研发出了一款可以日常携带的多功能小工具 <a href=\"https://www.tacticagear.com/#detail\" rel=\"nofollow\">Talon</a>——别因为它的大小就小瞧它，干净利落的一体式造型其实囊括了 17 种功能：开瓶器、度量尺、各种规格的扳手等工具应有尽有。它采用航空级的复合材料制成，重量较钛合金要轻 40%，无论你是要去远行还是放在身边以备不时之需都很合适。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/574773339/talon-ultra-lightweight-pocket-tool-for-everyday-c\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 30 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610302234345rIdjk2GemElQNL0.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561667\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030223437hGc81Wlwgv7IyuBC.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030223438e74xNU6fTaKiHYjl.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.555000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610302234403YxFGnlqr0IegSPy.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610302234395cuefAWlhMgOCJSx.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Ireland by B.Lux &amp; Stone Designs</h3><p>          </p><p>西班牙工作室 <a href=\"http://www.stone-dsgns.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stone Designs</a> 为灯具公司 <a href=\"http://www.grupoblux.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">B.Lux</a> 设计的 <a href=\"http://www.grupoblux.com/en/products/lamp-suspension/ireland.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ireland</a> 是一款由三个陶瓷灯罩组合而成的吊灯，每个灯罩的高度都可以进行调整，这种可变性使灯具散发出一种动态的感觉。设计师们的灵感来源于爱尔兰一处名为“巨人堤道”的景点，而陶瓷灯罩外部的三种哑光的色泽刚好让人联想到大地、石头和沙子，在灯光的配合下，给人一种低调舒适的视觉效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030224442EqB5DCSiI1W7YTlH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030224442UZ5lp1STaJ7CYxBo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.823611\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030224442C256UQKmfNZ8FwGp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.906944\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>X Air by Jeongchun Lee</h3><p>由牙买加雷鬼乐大师 Bob Marley 的家族创立的音响品牌 <a href=\"https://www.thehouseofmarley.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">The House of Marley</a> 大多使用自然环保以及可循环回收的材料，其中最常见的就是经过森林管理委员会认证的木材了。这款名为 X Air 的风扇就是韩国设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/chunny\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jeongchun Lee</a> 参照 The House of Marley 的产品风格所设计的概念产品，继承品牌的环保理念而加入的木材让风扇显得不那么冷冰冰了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030223514OHmTGyoPXcnjNQW4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639048\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030223513mcEoUGJ1Y4CngXp9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030223514FNfEHMTpxz5JnA3Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030223514xRKD9Hbgn5VuaEeU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161030223515JM6dHmeRuVYkLBfz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610302235156Pe70O48jl5rd1GV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639048\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}